INSERT INTO
    ais_positions (
        mmsi,
        latitude,
        longitude,
        course_over_ground,
        rate_of_turn,
        true_heading,
        speed_over_ground,
        TIMESTAMP,
        distance_to_shore,
        navigation_status_id
    )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],
        $2::DECIMAL[],
        $3::DECIMAL[],
        $4::DECIMAL[],
        $5::DECIMAL[],
        $6::INT[],
        $7::DECIMAL[],
        $8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
        $9::DECIMAL[],
        $10::INT[]
    )
ON CONFLICT (mmsi, TIMESTAMP) DO NOTHING
